<collectingCountry box="[449,559,1328,1354]" name="Suriname" pageId="19" pageNumber="478">Suriname</collectingCountry>
, and recently reported from 
<collectingCountry box="[875,990,1328,1354]" name="Venezuela" pageId="19" pageNumber="478">Venezuela</collectingCountry>
(
<bibRefCitation author="Perkins, P. D." box="[1004,1174,1328,1354]" pageId="19" pageNumber="478" pagination="1 - 59" refId="ref25400" refString="Perkins, P. D. (2019 c) Taxonomy of Venezuelan water beetles in the genus Hydrochus Leach, 1817, and an analysis of male genitalia morphology (Coleoptera: Hydrochidae). Zootaxa, 4708 (1), 1 - 59. https: // doi. org / 10.11646 / zootaxa. 4708.1.1" type="journal article" year="2019">Perkins, 2019c</bibRefCitation>
) and 
<collectingCountry box="[1236,1329,1328,1354]" name="Ecuador" pageId="19" pageNumber="478">Ecuador</collectingCountry>
(
<bibRefCitation author="Perkins, P. D." pageId="19" pageNumber="478" pagination="358 - 374" refId="ref25511" refString="Perkins, P. D. (2020 b) Taxonomy of Ecuadorian water beetles in the genus Hydrochus Leach, 1817 (Coleoptera: Hydrochidae). Zootaxa, 4790 (2), 358 - 374. https: // doi. org / 10.11646 / zootaxa. 4790.2.10" type="journal article" year="2020">Perkins, 2020b</bibRefCitation>
), the following specimen records are from 
<collectingCountry box="[717,809,1365,1391]" name="Panama" pageId="19" pageNumber="478">Panama</collectingCountry>
. Images of the habitus and male genitalia, and detailed description of the male genitalia of a specimen from 
<collectingCountry box="[742,857,1400,1426]" name="Venezuela" pageId="19" pageNumber="478">Venezuela</collectingCountry>
are given in 
<bibRefCitation author="Perkins, P. D." box="[1004,1185,1400,1426]" pageId="19" pageNumber="478" pagination="1 - 59" refId="ref25400" refString="Perkins, P. D. (2019 c) Taxonomy of Venezuelan water beetles in the genus Hydrochus Leach, 1817, and an analysis of male genitalia morphology (Coleoptera: Hydrochidae). Zootaxa, 4708 (1), 1 - 59. https: // doi. org / 10.11646 / zootaxa. 4708.1.1" type="journal article" year="2019">Perkins (2019c)</bibRefCitation>
.
</paragraph>
